Title: A Sassy Arathi
Description:
I had heard that an Arathi was making trouble in the city. It sounds like he is butting heads with the peacekeepers.

You've worked with the Arathi before, haven't you? Maybe you'd be able to smooth over any ruffled feathers.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Peacekeeper Leif in Dornogal.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Peacekeeper Leif in Dornogal.
RewardText: Yes, how can I help you?
